subject: Swimming
Olympic Games (2012)
lead_paragraph: Led by Missy Franklin, the American women won gold in the 4x100 medley relay. Sun Yang of China dethroned the defending champion Oussama Mellouli of Tunisia in the 1,500-meter freestyle.
